Welcome back to The Best & The Brightest. I=E2=80=99m Peter
Hamby.=C2=A0

=C2=A0

Tonight, my conversation with Illinois Governor J.B. Pritzker, one Democrat=
 seizing on his party=E2=80=99s current and ongoing leadership vacuum to at=
tack Donald Trump and make a name for himself in the early days of this new=
 administration. Pritzker=E2=80=94a likely 2028 presidential candidate=E2=
=80=94has much to say about how Democrats lost their way with middle-class
voters on issues like the economy and immigration. But less clear is how he=
=E2=80=94or any ambitious Democrat=E2=80=94can rival Trump=E2=80=99s total =
media dominance with kitchen table messaging about wages or retirement savi=
ngs.

=C2=A0

But first, a few updates from Abby Livingston and Dylan Byers=E2=80=A6

