 mostly hanging back and carefully picking their battles, Pritzker has sudd=
enly emerged as one of Trump=E2=80=99s loudest critics within the Democrati=
c Party, and an all-but-certain presidential candidate in 2028.=C2=A0</p><p=
 style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">I t=
alked to Pritzker by phone over the weekend about how to respond to
