his country were founded by immigrants or their children. <em>46 percent. <=
/em>The economy is dependent upon the entrepreneurship, the ingenuity, and =
the hard work of immigrants. We have that advantage in the world.
We=E2=80=99re used to immigration. We believe in immigration. You can=E2=80=
=99t walk down the street anywhere and not run into people who look differe=
nt than you, maybe have a slight accent or come from a different place. The=
